title: Output Parameter Not Displayed in Data Set Dialog
description: In the data set dialog, the output parameter is not being displayed as expected.
OB: The output parameter is not visible in the data set dialog when calling a stored procedure from an Oracle database.
EB: The output parameter should be clearly visible and displayed within the data set dialog when calling a stored procedure from an Oracle database.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the data set dialog.
2. Call a stored procedure from an Oracle database in the dialog.
3. Observe that the output parameter is not displayed as expected.
